<chapter id="Chapter574636">
  <title>CRM Module</title>
  <para>This module enables you to effectively organize Customer, Vendor, and
  other relationships in a centralized fashion. The system gives you the
  ability to store Addresses in a unified Address Book. It also enables you to
  track Incidents and To-Do's in a system-wide environment. The following
  topics will be covered in this chapter:</para>
  <itemizedlist>
    <listitem id="listitemN0x180ac00N0x1819e48">
      <para>Universal Address Book</para>
    </listitem>
    <listitem id="listitemN0x180ac00N0x1819e6c">
      <para>Accounts</para>
    </listitem>
    <listitem id="listitemN0x180ac00N0x1819e90">
